{"tid":1653011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比返工和理非都幫勇武做啲野","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T00:54:41.000Z","uid":333912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69d8d010d071cc111261b1ade968c9411520d3af","tid":1653011,"uid":333912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"就係做<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">掩護</span></span><br />\n而家既活動集中係禮拜六日同埋夜晚時間<br />\n但係黨鐵既早收同埋通街都係黑警<br />\n其實冇乜邊個敢出街<br />\n就算敢出街既和你非或者真街坊<br />\n好多都比黑警鳩搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家既假期同<span style=\"color: blue;\">戒嚴宵禁</span>相差無幾<br />\n出黎裝修塞路既效用同成本唔成比例<br />\n但係平日又會即刻平行時空 回復正常<br />\n其實香港最值錢既地方就係經濟活動<br />\n所以最好就係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大癮癮於市</span></span></span><br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">平日既時間做快閃</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做完即刻變返普通市民<br />\n始終係平日先會真正影響經濟<br />\n抵制個別企業雖然係有效<br />\n佢地間間市值都跌好多<br />\n其他企業都唔敢亂咁發聲<br />\n但咁樣又唔代表佢地唔會繼續奶共<br />\n美心咪又係繼續講商界唔敢發聲<br />\n或者有d暗地裡繼續奶到雪雪聲<br />\n同港共講話快d止暴制亂乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n最好就<span style=\"color: red;\">直接搞到香港既經濟</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁背後係香港拎利益既人先會知痛<br />\n就好似<span style=\"color: red;\">星期五</span>個活動希望會係個好開始<br />\n將抗爭融入日常生活<br />\n唔好比勇武同和理越行越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面呢個post會係個參考<br />\n<br />\n[核彈]已搵到港共政權既弱點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631166</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然情況已經唔同左<br />\n但佢講既<span style=\"color: blue;\">打擊經濟同越南游擊</span>值得諗諗<br />\n<br />\n最後我地唯一要諗既就係<br />\n咁做就係放全部香港人上枱<br />\n會唔會好似之前塞鐵咁比人屌曬鬼呢<br />\n同埋香港大混亂會唔會影響其他戰線<br />\n甚至老共就係想亂然後更大力鎮壓呢<br />\n我地可以再諗下有冇其他辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85aec40dca892f14b25d93471412ee76d1862540","tid":1653011,"uid":333912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"P牌仔新po自推"},{"pid":"42d8a820df93993939041400c3515203aef6c773","tid":1653011,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af51dae41d4768a6da11270713fa665a8ea74eef","tid":1653011,"uid":333912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"點推都冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774ed9bb28fe2e4a15ae30fd17ebb6e277ffcf93","tid":1653011,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"「直接搞到香港既經濟」呢句直接指出咁多個月嚟最失敗既地方<br />\n<br />\n老實講經濟一定係大春袋，你見之前搞機場政府個反應就知<br />\n<br />\n上星期都仲見到有人積極push下文宣，等大家有定一、兩個禮拜準備去三罷，依家好似無曬聲氣..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af54bf66fc7ec92d26c33b985b46c9d766b52a36","tid":1653011,"uid":333912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774ed9bb28fe2e4a15ae30fd17ebb6e277ffcf93","tid":1653011,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"「直接搞到香港既經濟」呢句直接指出咁多個月嚟最失敗既地方<br />\n<br />\n老實講經濟一定係大春袋，你見之前搞機場政府個反應就知<br />\n<br />\n上星期都仲見到有人積極push下文宣，等大家有定一、兩個禮拜準備去三罷，依家好似無曬聲氣..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"罷工罷極都罷唔起，所以手足先要去街頭流血<br />\n明明香港春袋就係經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要有d易入口既方法帶下個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得每樣野都要睇時機<br />\n而家民怨越黎越大<br />\n抗議日常化應該要帶起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人急需一場朝早嘅抗爭，以打破悶局！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647155</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n之前有人話星期五朝早行返工<br />\n如果帶得起個頭就有新方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120d9dd96a38bb33b400d7b3357b288b18a162c1","tid":1653011,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"62cb919d3fc7af28e383aaf5ca216bb8766b7422","tid":1653011,"uid":333912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120d9dd96a38bb33b400d7b3357b288b18a162c1","tid":1653011,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"Push!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起😭😭"}]}